<footer class="attribution">&mdash;&nbsp;<cite class="author">Erma Bombeck</cite></footer></blockquote><div class="erma-image-container"></div></div><div class="site-inner"><div class="content-sidebar-wrap"><main class="content" id="genesis-content"><section id="text-9" class="widget-odd widget-last widget-first widget-1 home-notice widget widget_text"><div class="widget-wrap"><h3 class="widgettitle widget-title">Seeking inspiring teachers</h3>
			<div class="textwidget"><p><img class="alignright wp-image-11828" src="http://humorwriters.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Erma_Marker_DavidBraughler-400x300.jpg" alt="" width="225" height="169" />We’re seeking top-notch faculty and session ideas for the April 2-4, 2020, Erma Bombeck Writers’ Workshop at the University of Dayton. Deadline for proposals is April 5, 2019, with prospective faculty notified by June 17 if their sessions have been selected. To submit a proposal, click on <a href="http://humorwriters.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Call-for-Faculty-Proposals.pdf">Call for Faculty Proposals</a>, fill out the form and email it to <a href="mailto:erma@udayton.edu">erma@udayton.edu</a>.</p>
