</div><footer class="entry-footer"></footer></article><article class="post-11944 post type-post status-publish format-standard category-news entry" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork"><header class="entry-header"><h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline"><a href="http://humorwriters.org/2019/01/31/up-yours-tidying-up/" rel="bookmark">Up yours, tidying up</a></h2>
</header><div class="entry-content" itemprop="text"><div class="at-above-post-homepage addthis_tool" data-url="http://humorwriters.org/2019/01/31/up-yours-tidying-up/"></div>
<p><img class="alignright wp-image-11615" src="http://humorwriters.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Laurie-OConnor-Stephans-head-shot-400x400.jpg" alt="" width="275" height="275" srcset="http://humorwriters.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Laurie-OConnor-Stephans-head-shot-400x400.jpg 400w, http://humorwriters.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Laurie-OConnor-Stephans-head-shot-100x100.jpg 100w, http://humorwriters.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Laurie-OConnor-Stephans-head-shot-768x767.jpg 768w, http://humorwriters.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Laurie-OConnor-Stephans-head-shot.jpg 889w" sizes="(max-width: 275px) 100vw, 275px" />We used to host two big gatherings every year: a huge cookout Memorial Day weekend and a &#8220;both sides of the family along with anyone who didn&#8217;t have anywhere else to go&#8221; Thanksgiving feast.<br />
The first and foremost reason for these events was because I love to entertain and truly believe the more the merrier.<br />
But the secondary reason had its own merits as well. By opening our home to throngs of people, the whole house got a good cleaning every six months. [&hellip;]<!-- AddThis Advanced Settings above via filter on get_the_excerpt --><!-- AddThis Advanced Settings below via filter on get_the_excerpt --><!-- AddThis Advanced Settings generic via filter on get_the_excerpt --><!-- AddThis Share Buttons above via filter on get_the_excerpt --><!-- AddThis Share Buttons below via filter on get_the_excerpt --></p>
